6:
All gathered? Great! Good morning,
everyone!
10:
So, um... What exactly are we here
for?
12:
It's simple. Sakura, Tae, I have a job
for you two.
26:
And I'm guessing you called the rest
of us here to help with that?
31:
Oh, not with the work itself. I need
someone to watch over Tae.
37:
Wait, explain yourself. I'm not sure 
I like where this is go—
41:
Sorry, gotta run! I have other
matters to tend to! The job details
are in this memo. Toodle-oo!
45:
It's been a while since we last got to
work together! Let's give it our all,
Tae-chan!
54:
Er, just to be sure... 
Is she going to be all right?
56:
I mean, can we be certain she won't
bite audience members during a
performance?
61:
Yeah, that can be a bit of a problem,
huh? Well, just consider it her way of
communicating.
66:
Are we really going to just leave it at
that?!
71:
Which reminds me: what's with the
nickname "Legendary Tae Yamada"?
76: Yeah, the word is she's a legend...
80:
Heck, does it really matter? 
Let's get a move on already.
86:
Hold it! I remain unconvinced that
this is a good idea!
89:
I look forward to your assistance
with today's product promotion
campaign!
92:
Thank you for the opportunity.This
is... deep-fried fish cake?
95:
Oh, you know of these things?
Tatsumi told me about 'em—in
exchange for the job!
96:
They're too good to not be snapped
up by everyone! Best of luck!
99:
So we'll be playing the role of sales
reps, huh...
103:
Will Tae be able to withstand the
aroma of fish cakes right in front of
her? It'd be a shame to have them
disappear into her mouth...
108:
S-sure! I think she can handle
it!...Probably!
115:
Thanks for the reassurance,
Tae-chan. So we're on the same
page then—absolutely no eating.
Good.
122:
Come try our crunchy new snack!
You're guaranteed to love it!
127:
Look how hard Tae's working. 
Guess we were worried for nothing.
131:
Perhaps you're right. 
I may have been overthinking it.
156:
What do I do?! Oh, I know! Nimbus!
Can you take Tae-chan's place?
164:
This is bad! Really bad! A head
bouncing around is going to freak
people out!
168:
They couldn't have gone far. 
If we just search the vicinity...
182:
Yeeoowch! Keep your teeth off my
hand, please!
189:
H-here you go, meow. Thank you
very much, meow.
193:
Sorry we're late! Hope there wasn't
too much of a panic here.
197:
Oh, we managed! Thanks for saving
Tae-chan!
204:
Phew, what a relief. By the way,
Nimbus, did you just say "meow"?
209:
I'm gonna forget you asked that,
and you're gonna forget you heard
anything! We clear?!
214:
Should Tae really be doing jobs
like this? Because I'm definitely
feeling uneasy.
218:
Ahaha... I'm sure it'll be okay next
time! Right, Tae?
